Package it.polimi.ingsw.common.backend.model.resourcetransactions

Class ResourceTransactionRecipe

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.common.backend.model.resourcetransactions.ResourceTransactionRecipe
public class ResourceTransactionRecipe extends Object
This class represents a recipe of a transaction of transfers of resources from and to resource containers and a player.

    • ResourceTransactionRecipe

      public ResourceTransactionRecipe​(Map<ResourceType,​Integer> input, int inputBlanks, Set<ResourceType> inputBlanksExclusions, Map<ResourceType,​Integer> output, int outputBlanks, Set<ResourceType> outputBlanksExclusions, boolean discardableOutput)
      Initializes the production specifying its input and its output.
      Parameters:
      input - the map of the resources to be given as input of the production
      inputBlanks - the number of the input blanks
      inputBlanksExclusions - the resources that cannot replace input blanks
      output - the map of the resources to be taken as output of the production
      outputBlanks - the number of the output blanks
      outputBlanksExclusions - the resources that cannot replace output blanks
      discardableOutput - true if the output can be discarded; false otherwise.
